1
00:00:07,560 --> 00:00:09,280
Gu Yixiao never imagined

2
00:00:09,640 --> 00:00:11,480
that the woman about to become his wife

3
00:00:11,840 --> 00:00:13,680
was wishing for his death every moment.

4
00:00:21,320 --> 00:00:22,320
But that's not enough.

5
00:00:24,760 --> 00:00:25,640
I want this too.

6
00:00:31,660 --> 00:00:35,700
=Half-awake=

7
00:00:35,780 --> 00:00:39,380
=Episode 22=

8
00:01:25,880 --> 00:01:28,160
(1, 2, 3, 6, 9, 0.)

9
00:01:28,800 --> 00:01:31,160
(What's the order?)

10
00:01:31,800 --> 00:01:33,680
(No way to test them all in time.)

11
00:01:34,320 --> 00:01:36,600
(Passwords are often dates.)

12
00:01:38,240 --> 00:01:40,000
(If that's the case,)

13
00:01:40,320 --> 00:01:42,290
(19603202.)

14
00:01:42,740 --> 00:01:44,320
(20190623.)

15
00:01:44,730 --> 00:01:45,820
(2019)

16
00:01:45,820 --> 00:01:47,500
(Donghua University, June 23, 2019)

17
00:01:48,800 --> 00:01:49,640
(Wait a second.)

18
00:01:50,560 --> 00:01:52,440
(The day I got my Letter of Admission.)

19
00:01:53,800 --> 00:01:54,880
(If he sees it)

20
00:01:54,880 --> 00:01:56,600
(as the start of his revenge...)

21
00:02:08,320 --> 00:02:10,120
(Why is there a gun?)

22
00:02:33,760 --> 00:02:34,600
Xingwan,

23
00:02:35,400 --> 00:02:36,720
did you find it?

24
00:02:39,520 --> 00:02:40,440
I...

25
00:02:43,360 --> 00:02:45,440
Just now, this cabinet opened
on its own.

26
00:02:46,080 --> 00:02:47,840
It revealed a safe inside.

27
00:02:48,200 --> 00:02:49,800
I was curious.

28
00:02:55,080 --> 00:02:56,600
Curious?

29
00:03:01,680 --> 00:03:03,640
So how did you know the code?

30
00:03:07,720 --> 00:03:09,880
I guessed.

31
00:03:10,760 --> 00:03:12,320
Pretty accurate guess.

32
00:03:16,480 --> 00:03:19,520
I should've known you'd figure it out.

33
00:03:20,280 --> 00:03:21,640
And that was the day

34
00:03:22,160 --> 00:03:24,000
your dream shattered.

35
00:03:28,360 --> 00:03:29,480
Such a shame.

36
00:03:29,720 --> 00:03:30,640
Inside here,

37
00:03:31,200 --> 00:03:32,440
there's no evidence against me.

38
00:03:35,720 --> 00:03:36,920
Are you disappointed?

39
00:03:38,390 --> 00:03:39,800
Why would I be?

40
00:03:41,240 --> 00:03:42,520
At least there's a gun in there.

41
00:03:43,600 --> 00:03:44,860
Illegal possession of a firearm.

42
00:03:45,320 --> 00:03:46,960
That's a serious charge, right?

43
00:03:57,560 --> 00:03:59,120
You mean this one?

44
00:04:04,760 --> 00:04:06,640
Then go ahead and report me now.

45
00:04:09,260 --> 00:04:10,360
Are you trying to end me?

46
00:04:10,880 --> 00:04:11,960
Ye Xingwan,

47
00:04:12,920 --> 00:04:14,600
you agreed to marry me.

48
00:04:14,920 --> 00:04:17,320
Yet you're still plotting
to see me gone.

49
00:04:18,040 --> 00:04:20,040
What's really going on in your mind?

50
00:04:20,480 --> 00:04:21,960
Do you think

51
00:04:22,760 --> 00:04:24,440
I should take you out?

52
00:04:36,880 --> 00:04:39,120
So you actually believe I'd hurt you.

53
00:04:43,750 --> 00:04:45,560
My right hand can't even pull a trigger.

54
00:04:46,660 --> 00:04:47,550
Did you forget?

55
00:04:48,520 --> 00:04:50,440
I risked everything
to save you back then.

56
00:04:55,560 --> 00:04:56,760
My hand was injured.

57
00:04:57,000 --> 00:04:58,750
My right-hand fingers
have no strength now.

58
00:05:03,480 --> 00:05:04,480
Here's your chance.

59
00:05:05,120 --> 00:05:06,520
Go ahead, end me.

60
00:05:07,160 --> 00:05:08,640
Achieve what you've been aiming for.

61
00:05:09,280 --> 00:05:10,200
I won't harms others.

62
00:05:10,560 --> 00:05:12,720
I won't use shady methods
to get my way unlike you.

63
00:05:13,040 --> 00:05:14,240
Since you already knew my plan,

64
00:05:15,840 --> 00:05:17,200
why didn't you stop me?

65
00:05:23,960 --> 00:05:25,120
I told you before,

66
00:05:26,320 --> 00:05:28,000
I'll make it up to you,

67
00:05:28,280 --> 00:05:30,320
to atone for the pain I once caused.

68
00:05:31,040 --> 00:05:32,640
So no matter what you do,

69
00:05:33,520 --> 00:05:35,200
I'll still forgive you.

70
00:05:53,280 --> 00:05:54,440
This is the only photo

71
00:05:54,440 --> 00:05:55,520
of the three of us.

72
00:05:57,320 --> 00:05:58,200
Back then,

73
00:05:59,400 --> 00:06:00,520
I was truly happy,

74
00:06:00,880 --> 00:06:02,080
genuinely content.

75
00:06:03,320 --> 00:06:06,040
Because I could really feel

76
00:06:06,920 --> 00:06:08,560
that I was loved.

77
00:06:10,200 --> 00:06:11,520
But,

78
00:06:12,800 --> 00:06:14,640
those days of happiness

79
00:06:16,120 --> 00:06:18,200
feel so far away now.

80
00:06:29,040 --> 00:06:30,080
Ye Xingwan,

81
00:06:32,480 --> 00:06:33,840
do you love me?

82
00:06:43,480 --> 00:06:45,760
Then let me ask it another way.

83
00:06:47,160 --> 00:06:48,280
If one day,

84
00:06:50,720 --> 00:06:52,360
I had to run for my life,

85
00:06:53,120 --> 00:06:55,040
would you stay with me?

86
00:07:19,600 --> 00:07:21,960
(You don't have to answer, Xingwan.)

87
00:07:22,920 --> 00:07:25,220
(Just let me stay by your side.)

88
00:07:27,160 --> 00:07:28,640
(All I ask is for one chance)

89
00:07:30,360 --> 00:07:31,480
(to be worthy of loving you.)

90
00:07:36,040 --> 00:07:37,720
(That hard drive is badly damaged.)

91
00:07:38,320 --> 00:07:39,720
(I only recovered a few fragments.)

92
00:07:40,000 --> 00:07:41,380
(Xiao Yinan)
(I sent them to you.)

93
00:07:48,900 --> 00:07:50,560
This is from the dash cam.

94
00:07:51,750 --> 00:07:52,640
It's pretty clear.

95
00:07:52,640 --> 00:07:54,240
They were chasing my dad.

96
00:07:54,840 --> 00:07:57,360
Gu Yixiao told me dad's death
was an accident.

97
00:07:58,400 --> 00:07:59,760
I didn't cause your dad's death.

98
00:08:00,480 --> 00:08:01,960
Back then, he owed me money.

99
00:08:02,220 --> 00:08:03,520
He couldn't pay and disappeared.

100
00:08:04,240 --> 00:08:05,090
Later on, I learned

101
00:08:05,100 --> 00:08:06,950
about the subsequent events
together with you.

102
00:08:07,420 --> 00:08:08,960
I admit I pushed him too hard back then.

103
00:08:09,330 --> 00:08:10,960
But I never meant him any harm.

104
00:08:11,200 --> 00:08:12,320
Now the truth is clear.

105
00:08:12,760 --> 00:08:13,720
It was an accident.

106
00:08:16,440 --> 00:08:17,640
What exactly happened?

107
00:08:39,180 --> 00:08:40,780
(Photo of Criminal Suspect)

108
00:08:40,800 --> 00:08:42,320
Chu Zhihao.

109
00:08:43,080 --> 00:08:43,960
I want this too.

110
00:08:47,840 --> 00:08:49,280
So that's how it is.

111
00:08:49,640 --> 00:08:50,960
Chu Muzhi is the son

112
00:08:50,960 --> 00:08:52,800
of the loan shark from years ago.

113
00:08:53,840 --> 00:08:54,680
Why?

114
00:08:56,080 --> 00:08:57,840
Why's he still working
along with Gu Yixiao?

115
00:08:59,220 --> 00:09:00,580
(Xiao Yinan)

116
00:09:03,160 --> 00:09:04,240
Hello? Yinan.

117
00:09:04,280 --> 00:09:05,000
Xingwan,

118
00:09:05,000 --> 00:09:06,520
has my sister contacted you these days?

119
00:09:06,520 --> 00:09:07,360
Nope.

120
00:09:07,800 --> 00:09:08,640
What's up?

121
00:09:09,240 --> 00:09:10,240
Has something happened?

122
00:09:10,600 --> 00:09:11,820
I can't get in touch with her.

123
00:09:11,960 --> 00:09:12,820
I heard from the nurse

124
00:09:12,830 --> 00:09:14,240
ever since the day before yesterday,

125
00:09:14,240 --> 00:09:15,690
she never came to the hospital again.

126
00:09:15,690 --> 00:09:16,940
Her phone's been turned off too.

127
00:09:17,300 --> 00:09:19,160
She would never just abandon my dad
like that.

128
00:09:20,970 --> 00:09:21,870
Yinan, wait a second.

129
00:09:21,870 --> 00:09:22,710
I'll be right there.

130
00:09:27,280 --> 00:09:29,320
This is the surveillance footage
from that day.

131
00:09:38,160 --> 00:09:39,240
(That back view...)

132
00:09:39,720 --> 00:09:40,800
(It's Chu Muzhi.)

133
00:09:41,960 --> 00:09:43,320
What's wrong, Xingwan?

134
00:09:45,400 --> 00:09:46,240
It's nothing.

135
00:09:47,000 --> 00:09:47,880
Keep playing it.

136
00:09:50,660 --> 00:09:52,010
(Could it be that he takes Qianyu)

137
00:09:52,010 --> 00:09:53,040
(to threaten me?)

138
00:09:54,040 --> 00:09:55,120
(He's too dangerous.)

139
00:09:55,560 --> 00:09:56,920
(I can't let Yinan take the risk.)

140
00:10:14,260 --> 00:10:17,180
♪The fragility stripped away by you♪

141
00:10:17,700 --> 00:10:20,660
♪Keeps dragging me down endlessly♪

142
00:10:21,300 --> 00:10:24,980
♪If not once devoured by blazing flames♪

143
00:10:24,980 --> 00:10:28,060
♪Who would ever understand
this baptism by fire♪

144
00:10:28,340 --> 00:10:31,260
♪You betrayed me so decisively♪

145
00:10:31,780 --> 00:10:34,700
♪With indifference laid bare♪

146
00:10:35,300 --> 00:10:38,300
♪It taught me to stay silent first♪

147
00:10:38,300 --> 00:10:41,780
♪So the explosion would be deafening♪

148
00:10:43,100 --> 00:10:48,860
♪A burning soul tears off
its own shackles♪

149
00:10:50,180 --> 00:10:51,980
♪The stubborn pain♪

150
00:10:51,980 --> 00:10:58,660
♪Hardens into the hottest flame♪

151
00:11:00,780 --> 00:11:05,340
♪Taste the fruit you planted,
don't ask me for mercy♪

152
00:11:05,340 --> 00:11:08,780
♪Just enjoy this searing pain♪

153
00:11:08,900 --> 00:11:12,140
♪See whether blood or tears flow first♪

154
00:11:12,260 --> 00:11:15,020
♪Your screams sound like regret to me♪

155
00:11:15,020 --> 00:11:19,460
♪Greed caused the chaos,
none can run away♪

156
00:11:19,460 --> 00:11:23,020
♪The karma you sowed by your own hands♪

157
00:11:23,020 --> 00:11:26,100
♪Watered to maturity
with blood and tears♪

158
00:11:26,340 --> 00:11:29,060
♪Then ignite the anger forged by hatred♪

159
00:11:29,060 --> 00:11:33,260
♪I'll burn it all down♪
